        <Parent_String>brass (alloy) [300010946], copper alloy [300010942], copper and copper alloy [300241441], nonferrous metal [300011014], metal by composition or origin [300010901], metal [300010900], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
